reviewText: Alessandro Safina means "everything", his voice is the best and this concert is simply BEAUTIFUL. I'd recommend to anyone who likes italian music. Love it !!!!

was looking for this dvd for 6 years. alessandro safina has a great voice and this concert is on a speciale place.
you dondt need to be a fan to love it!!!!!!!!!!
was happy to receive my DVD on time and in perfect shape. I love Alessandro Safina's voice and to actually see him in concert makes it even better. I just wish it was on Blue Ray.
